{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"690","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"女性勞工母性健康保護 勞動部下修適用企業門檻","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US'>2020-05-07 20:11 </span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>中央社</span><span lang='EN-US'>/</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>台北</span><span lang='EN-US'>7</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;&#10;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>日電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>勞動部今天表示，百人以上事業雇主，若其懷孕或產後一年女性勞工有從事對母性健康有為害之虞工作，除了應由醫師評估風險，並依結果調整工作措施外，也應訂母性健康保護計畫。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>現行「女性勞工母性健康保護實施辦法」規定，公司規模達</span><span lang='EN-US'>300</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>人以上的雇主，除必須對有母性健康危害之虞的工作，採取危害評估、控制及分級管理措施，同時須找醫師對於妊娠中或分娩後未滿一年的女性勞工，進行評估建議，並採取工作調整或更換等健康保護措施。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>不過，配合臨場醫護人員下修至</span><span lang='EN-US'>100</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>人以上企業應聘用特約醫護，勞動部今天也預告「女性勞工母性健康保護實施辦法」部分條文修正草案，將人數</span><span lang='EN-US'>300</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>人下修為</span><span lang='EN-US'>100</span><span style='font-family:&#10;&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>人，並要求雇主應訂定母性健康保護計畫。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>勞動部職安署職業衛生健康組組長張國明表示，母性健康保護涉及醫護專業，因此配合聘僱醫護門檻下修至事業單位勞工人數在</span><span lang='EN-US'>100</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>人以上，一併讓女性勞工母性健康保護實施辦法門檻下修至</span><span lang='EN-US'>100</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>人以上。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>張國明表示，對事業單位來說，這是屬於新措施，這次預告也要求雇主應該訂定母性健康保護計畫，因此給予雇主一些緩衝期，預計明年</span><span lang='EN-US'>3</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>月上路。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>張國明也提到，若企業不遵守相關規定，最高可罰新台幣</span><span lang='EN-US'>30</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;&#10;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin'>萬元，這次規定修正，估計新增</span><span lang='EN-US'>1000</span><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>多家企業適用。</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;新細明體&quot;,serif;mso-ascii-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:新細明體;&#10;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:&#10;minor-latin'>資料來源</span><span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/7238/4547283</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-05-08","clk_count":"112"}},"__N_SSG":true}